OL,3,C'Horrendous' sheep-worrying attacks
OL,4,Cleave farmer thousands out of pocket
OL,6,FDavid Williams, a sheep farmer, told
OL,7,FITV News' Richard Payne livestock
OL,8,Fworrying can cost farmers thousands
OL,10,FA farmer is imploring people to keep
OL,11,Ftheir dogs on leads while walking in
OL,12,Fthe countryside following a series of
OL,13,F"horrendous" attacks on his flock.
OL,15,FDavid Williams, a sheep farmer in
OL,16,FGloucestershire, has lost around 50
OL,17,Fsheep to livestock worrying in the
OL,18,Flast eight years.
