OL,3,C'Horrendous' sheep-worrying attacks
OL,4,Cleave farmer thousands out of pocket
OL,6,FMr Williams said he worries about the
OL,7,Frisk of attacks, which can have
OL,8,Fdevastating consequences for the
OL,9,Fbusiness.
OL,11,F"The money we've got tied up in this
OL,12,Fthing is unbelievable. It's #200 for a
OL,13,Fewe and a lamb. That's basically the
OL,14,Fbottom line. And if you lose a few,
OL,15,Fyou're soon into the thousands," he
OL,16,Fexplained.
OL,18,FAccording to recent data, the South
OL,19,FWest was the worst-hit region by cost
OL,20,Ffor dog attacks on livestock last year.
