OL,3,C'Horrendous' sheep-worrying attacks
OL,4,Cleave farmer thousands out of pocket
OL,6,FThe data from NFU Mutual revealed that
OL,7,Fthe loss of livestock cost farmers in
OL,8,Fthe region an estimated #359,000 in
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FMr Williams said he wants more people
OL,12,Fto take responsibility for their dogs
OL,13,Fwhile walking in the countryside.
OL,15,F"People have their dogs and go for a
OL,16,Fwalk in the country, and they walk
OL,17,Fwhere they like, do what they like,
OL,18,Fand when you challenge them, you are
OL,19,Fthe worst person in the world," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
