OL,3,C'Horrendous' sheep-worrying attacks
OL,4,Cleave farmer thousands out of pocket
OL,6,F"Livestock worrying," which includes
OL,7,Fdogs attacking, chasing, and barking
OL,8,Fat sheep, is already illegal.
OL,10,FGloucestershire Police has launched a
OL,11,Fnew campaign encouraging the public to
OL,12,Fkeep dogs on a lead in farmland to
OL,13,Fstop them from chasing livestock.
OL,15,FOperation Recall aims to educate the
OL,16,Fpublic on the impact of livestock
OL,17,Fworrying and is being backed by animal
OL,18,Fwelfare charities.
