OL,3,C'Horrendous' sheep-worrying attacks
OL,4,Cleave farmer thousands out of pocket
OL,6,FSarah Carr, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FNaturewatch Foundation, said it's a
OL,8,Fproblem which has been getting worse
OL,9,Fdue to the huge increase in dog
OL,10,Fownership during the pandemic.
OL,12,F"Now these dogs are two, three, four
OL,13,Fyears old, that's when you get the
OL,14,Fissues. They haven't had that
OL,15,Fsocialisation, they haven't had any
OL,16,Fexperience of how they should be
OL,17,Fbehaving," she explained.
